1. Supermarket ----
Create a hierarchy of classes to represent Supermarket products
Product (name, term of consumption, category - dairy, bakery, etc., price, quantity)
Goods (name, category - household chemicals, textiles, etc., price, quantity)
Create a Supermarket app
Adding a product (product) to the base (take into account that the goods in the database may be available or not)
Saving the product base (to the file)
Download the product base from the file
View products (items) sorted by category
Search for a specific product (product) with delivery of product information (product)
Deleting a specific product (product) from a database
